<%= render :partial => 'o_cms/categories/navigation' %>

<h2>New Category</h2>

<div class="row">
  <div class="col-md-4">
    <p>Guidelines for categories</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Make sure you add a name and some body content to your category</li>
      <li>The slug field will be dispayed in the navigation bar of your browser on the category page. It will be created if you don't enter one.</li>
      <li>Meta title and description will be automatically created based on your title and body content.</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
  <div class="col-md-8">
    <%= render partial: 'form', locals: { category: @category } %>
  </div>
</div>
